Emmanuelle Chaulet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emmanuelle_Chaulet 0 Emmanuelle Chaulet is a French actress. She starred in Eric Rohmer's 1987 comedy Boyfriends and Girlfriends and Jon Jost's 1990 film All the Vermeers in New York. Emmanuelle_Chaulet is a_French_actress .
